{"title":"Salma","link":"/en/wol/d/r1/lp-e/1200003804","html":"<span id=\"page841\" class=\"pageNum\" data-no=\"841\" data-before-text=\"841\"></span><strong>SALMA</strong>(Sal&#x2B9;ma).<strong>1. </strong>Descendant of Judah and ancestor of David. (<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/0/0\" data-bid=\"1-1\" class=\"b\">1Ch 2:3-5,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/0/1\" data-bid=\"1-2\" class=\"b\"> 9-15</a>) He is also called Salmon.<wbr>&#x2014;<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/1/0\" data-bid=\"2-1\" class=\"b\">Ru 4:12,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/1/1\" data-bid=\"2-2\" class=\"b\"> 18-22;</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/1/2\" data-bid=\"2-3\" class=\"b\"> Lu 3:32</a>; see <a class=\"it\" href=\"/en/wol/tc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/0\">SALMON</a>.<strong>2. </strong>Forefather of those who settled in places such as Bethlehem, Netophah, and Atroth-beth-joab. (<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/2/0\" data-bid=\"3-1\" class=\"b\">1Ch 2:51,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/2/1\" data-bid=\"3-2\" class=\"b\">&#xA0;54</a>) Salma was a son of Hur in the Calebite branch of Judah&#x2019;s genealogy.<wbr>&#x2014;<a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/3/0\" data-bid=\"4-1\" class=\"b\">1Ch 2:4, 5,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/3/1\" data-bid=\"4-2\" class=\"b\"> 9,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/3/2\" data-bid=\"4-3\" class=\"b\"> 18, 19,</a><a href=\"/en/wol/bc/r1/lp-e/1200003804/3/3\" data-bid=\"4-4\" class=\"b\"> 50,&#xA0;51</a>."}